## 🗄️ Configuração do Banco de Dados

### PostgreSQL (Local)
```bash
# Instale PostgreSQL
# macOS: brew install postgresql
# Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install postgresql postgresql-contrib

# Inicie o serviço
# macOS: brew services start postgresql
# Ubuntu: sudo service postgresql start

# Crie usuário e banco
createuser -d [username]
createdb [project_name]_development
```

### MySQL (Local)  
```bash
# Instale MySQL
# macOS: brew install mysql
# Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install mysql-server

# Configure o banco
mysql -u root -p
CREATE DATABASE [project_name]_development;
CREATE USER '[username]'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY '[password]';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON [project_name]_development.* TO '[username]'@'localhost';
```

### Docker (Automático)
```bash
# O docker-compose.yml já configura o banco
# Apenas execute:
docker-compose up -d database
```

